               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17890909-4-crimeloc20">Wood-street</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17890909-4-crimeloc20" type="placeName" value="Wood-street"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17890909-4-crimeloc20" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-4-off18 t17890909-4-crimeloc20"></join>; I lost the lead on the 21st of July last, about two o'clock; I am a <rs id="t17890909-4-viclabel21" type="occupation">painter</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890909-4-victim70 t17890909-4-viclabel21"></join>; I missed it between four and five.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17890909-4-person72">
                  ELIZABETH
                   CROUCH
               <interp inst="t17890909-4-person72" type="surname" value="CROUCH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-4-person72" type="given" value="ELIZABETH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890909-4-person72" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Atkinson; between two and three o'clock I watched the prisoner, and saw him take an earthen pot with twelve pounds weight of white lead ground in oil; he had worked in the morning for my master; he said he took it to mix it with other colour.</p>
               <p>Prosecutor. Before I went out I mixed what colour I thought would be wanted in the course of the day; they always take it out in pots; he had not done half an hour's work for me, and that was in stone colour; he had no orders from me to fetch any colour.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I went to dinner with another young fellow, and we got in liquor; and by the persuasion of the young man I went and fetched the white lead, not knowing what I was about.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17890909-4-verdict22" type="verdictDescription">
